{"tid":1636751,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"抑鬱六年好返好多 你問我答","createTime":"2019-10-07T20:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T16:33:40.000Z","uid":315181,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6191056cb40c731341088fc28027dad024ef3e61","tid":1636751,"uid":315181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:31:40.000Z","msg":"其實有開過另一個post講心理醫生同私家精神科<br />\n但冇乜人睇 又見到好多同路人喺抑鬱post圍爐<br />\n怕你地睇唔到對你地有幫助嘅資訊<br />\n嚟邊快問快答唔太長氣 想知多啲可以過之前個post<br />\n或者直接tg: abc1874<br />\n<br />\n有過<br />\n1. 分裂情感性障礙（Schizoaffective disorders），<br />\n即又精神分裂又有情緒問題<br />\n2. 躁鬱 (bipolar type II)<br />\n3. 抑鬱 (depression) <br />\n4. 壓力後群症 (PTSD) 有flash back, panic attack<br />\n<br />\n好咗好多，尤其Depression，我有至少六年<br />\n希望幫到大家，亦請大家高抬貴手，<br />\n唔好太冇禮貌，太惡死，我仲未完全好返的<br />\n純粹想幫到同路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4b2d2854304623f660a37b1b9bd61b52ac267c","tid":1636751,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:32:34.000Z","msg":"有時好唔開心<br />\n唔想同任何人交流<br />\n甚至有自殺想法（無實際行動既意欲）<br />\n<br />\n可以點令自己開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a9c83520533bac10f6f5498328ab223a86c90e","tid":1636751,"uid":275030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2858ca791150fee6e40d8956c0abffabc46fdd","tid":1636751,"uid":293667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T20:35:20.000Z","msg":"我都會成日唔開心<br />\n自己鑽牛角尖諗勁多野<br />\n有時會諗人生有咩意義 想死<br />\n我都懷疑自己有抑鬱"},{"pid":"8db11e0ad02dd29125a755cd8859e4eca17176a1","tid":1636751,"uid":276658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T22:18:17.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n我都好鍾意哥基<br />\n希望樓主一生快樂"},{"pid":"e6d664fc26b1370698f282d658f94c6d94c49022","tid":1636751,"uid":194015,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6191056cb40c731341088fc28027dad024ef